1247
01:30:05,688 --> 01:30:08,816
I haven't been comfortable
since the Dodgers left Brooklyn.

1248
01:30:10,593 --> 01:30:12,891
What's your favorite thing
you ever wore?

1249
01:30:12,995 --> 01:30:15,759
