1254
01:30:39,588 --> 01:30:41,556
Can I get you a size?

1255
01:30:45,494 --> 01:30:48,952
No, I'm going to
the women's suit department.

1256
01:30:50,132 --> 01:30:52,100
[Door Opens]

1257
01:31:00,576 --> 01:31:02,476
So?

1258
01:31:04,080 --> 01:31:08,483
- Jackie Kennedy?
