1306
01:34:16,005 --> 01:34:18,473
You ruined everything.

1307
01:34:20,009 --> 01:34:22,443
[Quietly]
I know.

1308
01:34:22,545 --> 01:34:25,070
What we had... was really special.

1309
01:34:28,651 --> 01:34:30,551
Oh, please! What we—

1310
01:34:34,290 --> 01:34:40,786
Because of you,
I have no idea where my sister is.

1311
01:34:40,896 --> 01:34:41,988
I can't reach her.
Her phone's cut off.

1312
01:34:42,097 --> 01:34:45,225
