What are you doing here?

1407
01:42:24,059 --> 01:42:26,755
You live here?
In an old folks home?

1408
01:42:28,530 --> 01:42:31,260
It's a retirement community
for active seniors.

1409
01:42:31,366 --> 01:42:34,631
Wait, so you—
you live with our grandmother?

1410
01:42:37,673 --> 01:42:40,198
How'd you find out about her?

1411
01:42:40,308 --> 01:42:44,267
I can't believe she wrote you
without telling me.

1412
01:42:46,248 --> 01:42:48,216
It's so sneaky.

1413
01:42:49,551 --> 01:42:52,645
Does it offend
your strict moral code?

1414
01:42:56,024 --> 01:42:58,288
So, how's it going for you down here?

1415
01:42:58,393 --> 01:43:01,851
Who's buying your cocktails?

1416
01:43:01,963 --> 01:43:03,931
No one.

1417
01:43:04,032 --> 01:43:06,626
Oh, no.
Is your mojo failing you already?

1418
01:43:06,735 --> 01:43:08,635
My mojo's fine.

1419
01:43:08,737 --> 01:43:11,399
I just haven't felt like drinking.

1420
01:43:11,506 --> 01:43:14,669
Right. Probably haven't
felt like stealing...

1421
01:43:14,776 --> 01:43:18,576
or lying or having sex
with inappropriate partners either.

1422
01:43:20,582 --> 01:43:24,643
- Did you come down here just to abuse me?
- [Door Shuts]

1423
01:43:24,753 --> 01:43:27,313
Maggie.! I hope you are prepared
to be exceedingly rich...

1424
01:43:27,422 --> 01:43:29,390
because I booked you within an—

1425
01:43:31,593 --> 01:43:33,493
Rose. Oh.

1426
01:43:36,998 --> 01:43:38,989
Oh, Rose.

1427
01:43:39,101 --> 01:43:41,126
Look at you.

1428
01:43:41,236 --> 01:43:43,568
Oh, look how lovely you are. Oh.

1429
01:43:43,672 --> 01:43:45,572
[Laughing]

1430
01:43:47,209 --> 01:43:49,905
Oh. Do you remember me?

1431
01:43:51,780 --> 01:43:53,714
Yeah.

1432
01:43:53,815 --> 01:43:55,840
I remember you too.

1433
01:43:55,951 --> 01:43:57,919
You-You're exactly the same.

1434
01:43:58,019 --> 01:44:00,544
Smiley and huggable and—

1435
01:44:01,690 --> 01:44:03,885
- Ooh, and engaged?
