1436
01:44:03,992 --> 01:44:05,892
Oh, yeah.

1437
01:44:05,994 --> 01:44:09,794
- Holy shit. To who?
- No one you know.

1438
01:44:09,898 --> 01:44:11,889
Champagne. Now, come with me.

1439
01:44:12,000 --> 01:44:14,696
Tell me all about it.

1440
01:44:18,006 --> 01:44:21,464
I can't believe you're marrying
somebody I haven't even met.

1441
01:44:26,314 --> 01:44:28,305
What's he like anyhow?

1442
01:44:31,953 --> 01:44:34,251
Why? You want to screw him too?

1443
01:44:38,660 --> 01:44:41,458
I don't expect you to forgive me, Rose...

1444
01:44:45,734 --> 01:44:47,702
