1445
01:44:55,110 --> 01:44:57,169
[Squeaky Horn Tooting]

1446
01:44:57,279 --> 01:44:59,747
- [Maggie] Careful, Mrs. Haskell.
- I'm always careful!

1447
01:44:59,848 --> 01:45:03,375
