It was a big to-do.

1448
01:45:03,485 --> 01:45:07,285
And there's a store where you can buy
eight different kinds of hemorrhoid creams.

1449
01:45:07,389 --> 01:45:09,653
All right.
Here come the Queen Bees.

1450
01:45:09,758 --> 01:45:13,250
